title: Do You Want To Play A Game?
body:
IceGame requires 7 players to start:
Entry fee- 0.05 BNB (to be paid prior to start)
Prize pool- Winning team splits entire pool + added bonuses
Rules- Every round players must vote or die... IN DEPTH RULES COMING SOON

Each player will begin with a 0.05 BNB bounty on their head
Each round players will get eliminated until one team secures victory and the riches!

Are you in?

Once 7 or more players have agreed to sign up we will begin playing 10/11/21
